ent <64 bound, but a regression to <32 would crash on Jenquai-Culture too); (d) m_Mutex deadlock if a regression moves the lock above the early-return guards. Per CLAUDE.md server-integrity: the wire shape is exactly what retail Win32 client emits when user clicks the \"+\" on a skill in the skill tree."),
